    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Titanium ore found in igneous rock and supplies a major portion of the world's titanium; source for titanium white pigment and used in ceramic glazes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
